The <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>only</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> zone I've ever had serious problems snaring on a regular basis in is Tactics.  For those situations, this is what you do.  Invest in an Orb of Tishan and a tola robe, and get haste from your nearby shaman/beastlord/bard etc.  It sounds cheesy, but it lands a fair MR debuff on the mob which is usually enough to make snaring a simple task.  You can even take a break to cast a nuke if you want, but it shouldn't take more than 15 seconds from the start of the fight with good haste, and you don't have to wait for the tank to build agro even.<br>
