<br>
The only other dmg dealing class I ever see offering as much utility as us is rangers. I often see them snare, root park, off-tank etc and I love that. The more flexible a group is the more they can cope when the train arrives or other unexpected events.<br>
<br>
We are a flexible class even if it's simply stunning a mob that has jumped the chanter after a resisted slow. Yeah I could do over twice the dmg with AT (for almost twice the mana, Telekin is less than 25% more efficient) but I'm saving the cleric 400+ mana in heals too. 8 sec of a mob beating on a robe can be a *lot* of group mana saved. Even if the cleric is simply bubbling with mana he can nuke with his 400 mana instead and the *group* does more dmg to the mob. It's a synergie we can fit well into. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> <b>5</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=27003.topic&start=121&stop=137>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=27003.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=27003.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=27003.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.